title: Darwin's Doubt and Intelligent Design - Collection 10
description:
Darwin's Doubt and Intelligent Design - Collection 10:

We have 22 titles here:

-  Barnard - Social Anthropology and Human Origins (2011)

-  Brasier - Secret Chambers; the Inside Story of Cells & Complex Life (2012)

-  Carneiro - Evolutionism in Cultural Anthropology; a Critical History (2003)

-  Cohen - Equations from God; Pure Mathematics and Victorian Faith (2007)

-  Comfort & Seto - Man's Indiscriminate Stealing of God's Amazing Design (2012)

-  Dembski & Wells - The Design of Life; Discovering Signs of Intelligence in Biological Systems (2008)

-  Denton - Evolution; Still a Theory in Crisis (2016)

-  Derr - How the Dog Become the Dog; From Wolves to Our Best Friends (2011)

-  Franses - Time, Light and the Dice of Creation; Through Paradox in Physics to a New Order (2015)

-  Goswami - Creative Evolution; a Physicist's Resolution between Darwinism & Intelligent Design (2008)

-  Haught - God After Darwin; a Theology of Evolution, 2e (2008)

-  Huntley - The Divine Proportion; a Study in Mathematical Beauty (1970)

-  Klinghoffer (Ed.) - Metamorphosis; the Case for Intelligent Design in a Nutshell Chrysalis (2011)

-  Land & Nilsson - Animal Eyes, 2e (2012)

-  Marshall - Evolution 2.0; Breaking the Deadlock between Darwin and Design (2015)

-  Midgley - The Solitary Self; Darwin and the Selfish Gene (2010)

-  Monton - Seeking God in Science; an Atheist Defends Intelligent Design (2009)

-  Peacocke - Paths from Science Towards God; the End of All Our Exploring (2013)

-  Rothman - The Paradox of Evolution; the Strange Relationship Between Natural Selection and Reproduction (2015)

-  Sober - Evidence and Evolution; the Logic Behind the Science (2008)

-  Thompson - Where Do Camels Belongs; the Story and Science of Invasive Species (2014)

-  Yahya - Devotion Among Animals; Revealing the Work of God (2004)
